WEBVTT

00:00.752 --> 00:01.917
- (gunshots) (tires squealing)
- _

00:01.986 --> 00:03.450
FALCO: What's this about
needing the bike back?

00:03.484 --> 00:04.285
BULLET: We're done.

00:04.355 --> 00:06.121
Operation's over.

00:06.190 --> 00:07.355
BULLET: Here to see The Devil.

00:07.424 --> 00:09.157
THE DEVIL: You begging or selling?

00:09.227 --> 00:10.156
BULLET: Offering.

00:10.156 --> 00:12.327
THE DEVIL: How about
I make <i>you</i> an offer?

00:12.396 --> 00:14.195
BULLET: They think I can help
em expand their footprint

00:14.263 --> 00:15.596
here in Petersburg.

00:15.666 --> 00:19.000
In terms of gathering evidence,
it'd be like shooting fish in a barrel.

00:19.068 --> 00:21.035
BULLET: The video feeds run 24/7.

00:21.103 --> 00:23.371
All recorded onto these drives.

00:23.440 --> 00:24.972
SARAH JANE:
I've been feeling kind of sick lately.

00:26.443 --> 00:28.242
THE DEVIL: I only count three.
Where's the fourth?

00:28.310 --> 00:29.542
BULLET: You'll meet him soon.

00:29.611 --> 00:30.945
THE DEVIL: Let's hope so,

00:31.013 --> 00:33.546
'cause next week your time is up.

00:33.615 --> 00:34.715
DARKO: Hey, Quick.

00:35.317 --> 00:37.735
- ♪
- _

00:37.737 --> 00:39.237
- ♪
- _

00:39.289 --> 00:41.956
- ♪
- _

00:42.024 --> 00:43.723
<i>CHARLES FALCO: Everyone
wants to feel there's somewhere</i>

00:43.792 --> 00:45.993
<i>in the world they're safe.</i>

00:46.060 --> 00:49.412
<i>For bikers that place is
supposed to be their clubhouse.</i>

00:51.100 --> 00:53.366
<i>Problem is, once you have a clubhouse</i>

00:53.435 --> 00:55.435
<i>your enemies know where to find you.</i>

00:55.505 --> 00:59.372
♪

00:59.442 --> 01:02.109
- ♪
- _

01:02.176 --> 01:06.739
<i>FALCO: On July 4th, 1979,
one Outlaws chapter boss arrived</i>

01:06.774 --> 01:10.284
<i>to discover his club had been subjected</i>
<i>to a brutal attack.</i>

01:10.352 --> 01:13.920
♪

01:13.989 --> 01:15.522
<i>FALCO: The Independence Day
massacre was one of the bloodiest</i>

01:15.590 --> 01:18.625
<i>acts of biker violence
in American history.</i>

01:18.692 --> 01:22.561
♪

01:22.631 --> 01:24.697
♪

01:24.765 --> 01:26.331
<i>FALCO: Ever since,
every new Outlaws clubhouse</i>

01:26.400 --> 01:30.168
<i>has been a fortress.</i>

01:30.237 --> 01:33.371
<i>But make no mistake,
if you put on the Outlaws patch,</i>

01:33.442 --> 01:35.441
<i>there's nowhere you'll ever be safe.</i>

01:37.677 --> 01:42.247
♪

01:42.317 --> 01:45.251
♪

01:45.319 --> 01:48.253
♪

01:48.323 --> 01:50.389
♪

01:50.457 --> 01:53.390
♪

01:53.460 --> 01:55.493
♪ Bite down
You gotta blow it up ♪

01:55.563 --> 01:58.263
♪ You gotta give it hell
You gotta pull the plug ♪

01:58.331 --> 02:00.599
♪ You can run away
You can kill the beast ♪

02:00.668 --> 02:03.902
♪ You can try to kill yourself
But you can never kill me ♪

02:03.971 --> 02:08.538
♪ Hey,
if this is how the world will end ♪

02:08.608 --> 02:12.543
♪ You can burn it again
'Cause we will not go quietly ♪

02:12.611 --> 02:17.014
♪ You can burn it again
'Cause we will not go quietly ♪

02:18.050 --> 02:19.183
(tapping on door)

02:19.252 --> 02:22.652
(muffled water running)

02:24.457 --> 02:25.455
FALCO: You okay?

02:25.525 --> 02:28.025
SARAH JANE: I'm great, I just...

02:28.093 --> 02:30.627
prefer not seeing my food
again after I've eaten it.

02:30.697 --> 02:31.662
FALCO: We can cancel later,

02:31.730 --> 02:33.531
and just get some pizza and chill.

02:33.599 --> 02:35.500
SARAH JANE: No, we have to go.

02:35.567 --> 02:38.703
I lived with Casey and Martha.
They're like family to me.

02:38.771 --> 02:41.504
They've asked about you,
like, a million times.

02:41.573 --> 02:43.173
FALCO: Oh, yeah?

02:43.241 --> 02:44.707
And what have you told them?

02:44.776 --> 02:47.377
SARAH JANE: Just that you live
locally and you do tree work.

02:47.445 --> 02:50.046
FALCO: That's all?

02:50.115 --> 02:51.615
SARAH JANE: Yeah, that's all.

02:53.352 --> 02:55.585
BULLET: Yes, sweety,
I will try and make it.

02:55.653 --> 02:57.221
(engine approaching)

02:57.288 --> 02:59.354
BULLET: Listen, I gotta go. I love you.

03:03.127 --> 03:04.293
(Bullet sighs)

03:07.465 --> 03:10.233
♪

03:10.300 --> 03:11.668
BULLET: Shit...

03:14.271 --> 03:15.437
BULLET: What's goin' on?

03:15.507 --> 03:17.340
SNIPER: Clean lookin' set of tools.

03:17.408 --> 03:18.908
You been working lately?

03:18.975 --> 03:19.908
BULLET: Oh, you here
'cause you're worried

03:19.977 --> 03:21.411
about my business?

03:21.478 --> 03:23.611
SNIPER: I'm here because you
need to open your clubhouse.

03:23.681 --> 03:25.048
BULLET: It's not finished.

03:25.115 --> 03:27.283
Besides, I thought we had
till the end of the month.

03:27.352 --> 03:29.352
SNIPER: What you have is an
hour to get everything ready,

03:29.420 --> 03:31.420
or else you can forget
ever becoming an Outlaw.

03:31.487 --> 03:33.688
(starts engine)

03:36.593 --> 03:39.929
(phone ringing)

03:39.997 --> 03:43.098
(phone ringing)

03:43.387 --> 03:46.155
FALCO: Hey. What's up?

03:46.223 --> 03:47.222
Are you serious?

03:48.858 --> 03:51.325
Look, I got... Okay.

03:51.395 --> 03:55.362
Alright, alright. I'll see you there.

03:55.432 --> 03:58.365
SARAH JANE: Let me guess,
something came up.

03:58.435 --> 04:01.134
FALCO: Yeah, I gotta meet Bullet.

04:01.204 --> 04:02.770
SARAH JANE: You're <i>not</i> going?

04:02.838 --> 04:04.671
Charlie, I told Martha
we'd be there at 2.

04:04.740 --> 04:05.907
FALCO: Look, I know.

04:05.974 --> 04:07.240
It shouldn't take more
than a couple hours.

04:07.310 --> 04:09.376
SARAH JANE: It shouldn't, or it won't?

04:09.444 --> 04:12.712
FALCO: Look, I'm sorry.
I just gotta do this one thing.

04:14.650 --> 04:16.454
SARAH JANE: Okay...

04:18.288 --> 04:20.288
I need you for this one thing.

04:20.355 --> 04:22.389
FALCO: I know, don't worry.

04:22.457 --> 04:26.660
♪

04:26.728 --> 04:30.430
♪

04:30.499 --> 04:31.432
(Sarah Jane sighs)

04:31.500 --> 04:36.269
♪

04:36.338 --> 04:41.274
♪

04:41.343 --> 04:46.146
♪

04:46.215 --> 04:49.882
♪

